Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:31.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:41.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:46.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:51.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:06.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:16.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:19.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:28.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:29.27,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
